      "rationale": "Titanium alloy Ti-6Al-4V modeled with bilinear isotropic hardening; elastic modulus and yield stress from ASM handbook. Contact at screw-rod interface modeled as frictional (mu=0.2) with penalty formulation. Sensitivity analysis showed QoI insensitivity to friction coefficient variation ±0.1. Model form consistent with prior FDA validation studies. Achieved level meets required level."
