      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories. All specimens drawn from production lots with full dimensional and material traceability. Coefficient of variation in stiffness across specimens was 6.3%, consistent with expected manufacturing variability. Sample size sufficient for statistical comparison at Medium risk level. Achieved level meets required level."
