      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span the range of anticipated clinical use conditions including at least two load levels or construct configurations.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 static compression-bending condition (axial offset load). No additional load levels or angulation conditions were evaluated. This limits the breadth of validation evidence relative to the full clinical use envelope. Achieved level (2) is below required level (3); this gap is acknowledged and accepted given the Medium model influence and the conservative nature of the F1717 protocol relative to in vivo loading."
