      "rationale": "FEA model geometry updated to match each specimen's measured dimensions where dimensional variation exceeded 0.05 mm. Material properties assigned from lot-specific mill certificates matched to each specimen's production lot. Boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry as confirmed by fixture drawings. Equivalency between model inputs and physical test conditions confirmed. Achieved level meets required level."
    },
    {
