      "rationale": "E/uval computed for all three primary QoIs: stiffness (0.81), yield force (1.12), and force at 40 mm displacement (1.44). All values below 1.96 threshold. Percent differences of 4.2%, 6.8%, and 7.9% respectively, all within the 10% acceptance bound. Quantitative output comparison confirms model predictive capability for all three QoIs. Achieved level meets required level."
